'''David Arkenstone''' ([[1 July|July 1]], [[1952]]) is a musician known for his fantasy themed music. He released an album titled [[Music Inspired by Middle Earth]] in [[2001]] which was filled with [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]-related songs.
